# Angular2-App
- this app is a getting started application for angular 2 it has features like show list of products, products details, filter product by name, and getting product data using http.
- it covers all the masure concepts of angular 2 including (modules, components, data binding, pipes, decorators, interfaces and more)
- this app was built as a practicing on this course
https://www.pluralsight.com/courses/angular-2-getting-started-update
Note:
you should have these requirements on your machine
1- node.js and npm.
2- typescript.
3- run npm install
- finally to see the final application go to /APM directory in terminal then type
# npm start


